name: QuyntessSupplyChainManagementDashboardSandbox
0:
”Alexa, start Quyntess Sandbox Dashboard”
”Alexa, start Quyntess Sandbox Dashboard and give me my daily updates.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: quyntess sandbox dashboard
des:
This skill allows Alexa to retrieve quick statistics and daily updates from your Quyntess Supply Chain dashboard. You can use this to:
- Retrieve your daily update, which returns the new, buyer modified and confirmed orders.
- Specifically ask for the current amount of new and buyer modifiedorders.
Attention, this skill connects to the Sandbox environment, thus for demo / tests purposes only.
